                  | Hello, my name is Pil. I started working on the web using Wordpress to create a fully functional website without any knowledge of complex languages. Interest in the web development soon motivated me to learn essential Front End languages such as HTML, CSS, and Javascript. Since then, I have been developing creative and easy-to-use but useful web applications and pages. Not only that I am well versed in Front End technologies, but I have been working with Back End technologies using Node.js and its frameworks, eager to master relevant languages to become a skillful Full Stack Developer. 
                  br
                  br
                  |                             When I am not working on projects, I bet you will find me either tweaking with Raspberry Pi to develop my own private cloud, hiking natural wonders of the Southwest, watching European football (soccer to many), or anything else I find interesting.
                  br
                  br
                  |                             I also have extensive experience and high interest in video editing with voiceover, photo editing, and working for local charities and non-profit organizations for a good cause. If you have a project idea in mind, shoot me a message and I will try to get back to you as soon as possible.
